info.description:
Rating Data Service stores information related to data points in a rate request. It contains questions, default values, requiredness, value lists, and rules. These are stored in hierarchical format, based on the shape of the request. 
Note that the hierarchy is not specific to any service, and may be created at will. The top level ApiTypeV1 is the base type of the user's request.
info.title: Rating Data Service
